NG0564:2: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la /
NG0564:3: sdig can phur ka zlog byed pa'i //
NG0564:4: ban d+he dam nyams bsgral ba'i thabs //
NG0564:5: legs bar bdag la bshad du gsol //
NG0564:8: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NG0564:9: sdig can dam nyams phur bzlog mkhan //
NG0564:10: gshin rje 'char ka nag po'i thugs kyi /
NG0564:12: sdig can myur du rang gshed 'khor //
NG0564:13: de bas khyed kyis legs par nyon la yid la zung */
NG0564:15: stegs bu gru bzhi nag po'i steng du /
NG0564:17: gshin rje 'char ka nag po'i gzugs byas la /
NG0564:19: g.yon du zhags pa bskur la /
NG0564:20: rang ting nge 'dzin dang ldan pas /
NG0564:21: sha khrag gi gtor mas bskong zhing */
NG0564:22: zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig bsnyen pa bskyal lo //
NG0564:23: de yang rang ma 'bags par kho'i dri ma la ling ka bya /
NG0564:24: de nas gro ga la yang bris la /
NG0564:26: dpung pa g.yas pa ma rus bris la snying kar gzhug / de'i tshe zhags pas bcings la /
NG0564:27: rdo rje mnan cing brdeg go / tha de tshe khong gi phyogs su /
NG0564:28: las kyi gshin rje'i 'og tu bcug la mnan no //
NG0564:29: thugs kyi 'khor lo'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o ///
NG0564:33: las kyi gshin rje bzhi'i sku mdog dang phyag mtshan legs par bshad du gsol /
NG0564:36: kye gshin rje 'char ka nag po 'di mdog gnag la 'tsher ba char sprin nag por 'ong */
NG0564:37: mdog las mi 'da' mtshan du btags pa 'char ka nag po zhes bya /
NG0564:38: dbu la dar nag gi tod bcings pa /
NG0564:39: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i rtags su /
NG0564:40: mchod rten gsum dang ldan pa /
NG0564:41: dar nag gi ber gyon pa /
NG0564:42: lus la sbrul 'jug rab tu 'khyil ba /
NG0564:43: spyan me stag gi phung po 'dra ba /
NG0564:44: mche ba gtsigs shing kha 'dangs ba /
NG0564:45: shin tu khro zhing rngam par bsgom mo //
NG0564:46: shan pa ban d+he nag po ni /
NG0564:48: dar nag gi cod pan can /
NG0564:52: mtshon gyi gru gu can no //
NG0564:54: dmar nag lcags kyi sbar shad can no //
NG0564:55: zhang blon mthing ka / ral gri can no //
NG0564:56: mon pa ljang nag / gri gug dang sbrul zhags can no //
NG0564:57: gzhan yang de'i 'khor na bdud dang */
NG0564:59: ma mo bal mos bskor ba'o //
NG0564:60: gshin rje 'char ka nag po rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NG0564:61: lha bsgom pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o //  // yang bka' stsal pa /
NG0564:62: gshin rje 'char ka nag po bsad pa'i man ngag
NG0564:63: / bdud kyi rwa zor nag po dang sbyar te
NG0564:64: gsod na / ngas bshad do legs par nyon cig / gang zhig mthu bo che dang 'gras na /
NG0564:65: til mar gyis ling ga byugs la /
NG0564:72: nam phar phyed tshul phyed na /
NG0564:73: yugs sa mos gtor na rab /
NG0564:74: med na rang nyid bdud chas su zhugs la gtor /
NG0564:75: zor yo dril ba'i sngags la /
NG0564:76: om ha de mo ha hri da ya pra ha ra na /
NG0564:79: sa ma ya a ti kra ma bzlog bzlog / a la la pra ma he /
NG0564:80: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yohzhes bzlas te gtor ro //
NG0564:81: pha mtshan gyi zor la bzlog na /
NG0564:82: khrag dang nyungs kar gyis bya'o //
NG0564:83: bdud kyi rwa zor gyi le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o ///
